es/my-first-custom-author-template.php %7s .','Copy the generated code and paste it inside the newly created file.'=>'Daakọ koodu ti a ṣe ati lẹẹmọ sinu faili tuntun ti a ṣẹda.','Congratulations. Your can now choose your template inside the PublishPress Authors Settings.'=>'E ku oriire. O le bayi yan àpẹẹrẹ rẹ laarin Awọn Eto PublishPress Authors.','You can read more information on the %s.'=>'O le ka alaye diẹ sii lori %s.','documentation page'=>'oju-iwe iwe itọsọna','Generate Template'=>'Ṣẹda Àkọsílẹ','Template generated successfuly!'=>'Àtẹ̀jáde àtẹ́yẹ̀wò ni aṣeyọrí!','Reorder Fields'=>'Tun Ṣeto Awọn aaye','Reorder the fields by dragging them to the correct position and saving your changes.'=>'Tunṣe awọn aaye nipasẹ gbigbe wọn si ipo to tọ ki o si fipamọ awọn ayipada rẹ.','Save for Current Author Box'=>'Fipamọ fun Apoti Akọwe Tẹlẹ','Save for All Author Boxes'=>'Fipamọ fun Gbogbo Awọn Apoti Akọwe','Select %1s'=>'Yan %1s','Change %1s'=>'Yipada %1s','Remove %1s'=>'Yọ %1s','Search %1s Icon'=>'Wa %1s Aami','New Author Categories Box'=>'Ibo Awon Onkọwe Tuntun','PublishPress Authors Pro allows you to unlock the full potential of Author Categories.'=>'PublishPress Authors Pro gba ọ laaye lati ṣii agbara kikun ti Awọn ẹka Onkọwe.','You can create Author Boxes where Authors are grouped into their categories.'=>'O le ṣẹda Awọn Apoti Onkọwe nibiti awọn Onkọwe ti wa ni ẹgbẹ sinu awọn ẹka wọn.','PublishPress Authors Box'=>'Aago Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress','Select an author box'=>'Yan apoti onkọwe kan','An error occured.'=>'Aṣiṣe kan ṣẹlẹ.','You do not have permission to perform this action'=>'O ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣe iṣe yii','Field Order updated. %1sClick here%2s to reload this page to see new order changes.'=>'Aṣẹ aaye ti ni imudojuiwọn. %1sTẹ nibi%2s lati tunṣe oju-iwe yii lati wo awọn ayipada titun aṣẹ.','Boxed'=>'Apoti','Boxed Right'=>'Apoti Otun','Centered'=>'Aarin','Inline'=>'Ni ila','Inline with Avatars'=>'Ni ila pẹlu Avatars','Simple List'=>'Atokọ Rọrun','Show Box Title'=>'Fih