 Onkọwe ni otun','Author Box Padding Top'=>'Iwọn Padi Àpoti Onkọwe ni oke','Author Box Padding Bottom'=>'Iwọn Padi Àpoti Onkọwe ni isalẹ','Author Box Padding Left'=>'Iwọn Padi Àpoti Onkọwe ni osi','Author Box Padding Right'=>'Iwọn Padi Àpoti Onkọwe ni otun','Author Box Border Width (px)'=>'Iwọn Ààrẹ Àpoti Onkọwe (px)','Author Box Border Style'=>'Ìṣàkóso Ààrẹ Àpoti Onkọwe','Author Box Border Color'=>'Àwọ̀ Ààrẹ Àpoti Onkọwe','Author Box Width (%)'=>'Iwọn Atokọ Onkọwe (%)','Author Box Border Radius (px)'=>'Iwọn Ààrẹ Àpoti Onkọwe (px)','Author Box Background Color'=>'Àwọ̀ Àpoti Onkọwe','Author Box Color'=>'Àwọ̀ Àpoti Onkọwe','Author Box Shadow Color'=>'Àwọ̀ Aaye Onkọwe','Author Box Shadow Horizontal Offset'=>'Ìkànsí Aaye Onkọwe Ti O Rọ','Author Box Shadow Vertical Offset'=>'Ìkànsí Aaye Onkọwe Ti O Giga','Author Box Shadow Blur'=>'Fọto Aaye Onkọwe','Author Box Shadow Spread'=>'Ìtẹ̀sí Aaye Onkọwe','Add Custom CSS styles here...'=>'Ṣe afikun awọn aṣa CSS adani nibi...','Layout Wrapper Class Name'=>'Orukọ Kilasi Wrapper Ilana','You can use multiple class names. Leave a space between each class.'=>'O le lo orukọ kilasi pupọ. Fi aaye silẹ laarin kilasi kọọkan.','Enter class name without dot(.)'=>'Tẹ orukọ kilasi laisi dot(.)','Add support for author categories.'=>'Fi atilẹyin fun awọn ẹka onkọwe.','Number of items per page'=>'Iye awọn nkan fun oju-iwe kọọkan','Singular name is required.'=>'Orukọ ẹyọkan jẹ dandan.','Plural name is required.'=>'Orukọ ipo jẹ dandan.','Author category with this name already exist.'=>'Ẹka onkọwe pẹlu orukọ yii ti wa tẹlẹ.','Category added.'=>'Ẹka ti a fi kun.','Error inserting new author category.'=>'Aṣiṣe ni fifi ẹka onkọwe tuntun si.','All fields are required.'=>'Gbogbo awọn aaye jẹ dandan.','Error updating category data.'=>'Aṣiṣe ni imudojuiwọn data ẹka.','Security error. Kindly reload this page and try again.'=>'Aṣiṣe aabo. Jọwọ tun ṣe ikojọpọ oju-iwe yii ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansi.','Invalid form data.'=>'Data fọọmu ti ko tọ.','Category order updated.'=>'Atilẹyin ẹka ti ni imudojuiwọn.','Search Author Categories'=>'Wa Awọn ẹka Akọwe','Add Author Category'=>'Fi Ẹka Onkọwe kun','Singular Name'=>'Orukọ Ẹyọkan','Enter the Author Category name when it\'s a single author'=>'Tẹ orukọ Ẹya Onkọwe nigbati o ba jẹ onkọwe kan ṣoṣo','Plural Name'=>'Orukọ Ipo','Enter the Author Category name when there are more than 1 author'=>'Tẹ orukọ Ẹya Onkọwe nigbati awọn onkọwe ju 1 lọ','Schema Property'=>'I Properties Schema','Example: when this value is set to reviewedBy, all users in this category will be added to post\'s reviewedBy property. You can read more %1$s in this guide.%2$s'=>'Apẹẹrẹ: nigbati iye yii ba ṣeto si reviewedBy, gbogbo awọn olumulo ni ẹka yii yoo jẹ afikun si ohun-ini reviewedBy ti ifiweranṣẹ. O le ka diẹ sii %1$s ninu itọsọna yii.%2$s','Post Types'=>'Iru Ifiweranṣẹ','Select Post Type...'=>'Yan Iru Ifiweranṣẹ...','Select which post types this category applies to. Leave empty for all post types.'=>'Yan iru awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti ẹka yii lo. Fi silẹ silẹ fun gbogbo awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ.','Enable Category'=>'Muu Ẹya ṣiṣẹ','Add New Author Category'=>'Ṣe afikun Ẹka Onkọwe Tuntun','Coauthor'=>'Onkọwe','Coauthors'=>'Awọn onkọwe','Reviewer'=>'Atunwo','Reviewers'=>'Awọn ayẹwo','Editor'=>'Onkọwe','Editors'=>'Awọn Onkọwe','Slug'=>'Slug','Enable Categories'=>'Muu Awọn Ẹya ṣiṣẹ','Disable Categories'=>'Kó Awọn Ẹka kuro','Author categories deleted successfully.'=>'Ìkànsí Onkọwe ti parẹ́ ni aṣeyọri.','Author category deleted successfully.'=>'Ìkànsí Onkọwe ti parẹ́ ni aṣeyọri.','Author categories enabled.'=>'Ìkànsí Onkọwe ti ṣiṣẹ́.','Author category enabled.'=>'Ẹka onkọwe ti ṣiṣẹ.','Author categories disabled.'=>'Ìkànsí Onkọwe ti dènà.','Author category disabled.'=>'Ẹka onkọwe ti pa.','No author categories.'=>'Ko si awọn ẹka onkọwe.','Quick edit &#8220;%s&#8221; inline'=>'Ṣatunkọ yara &#8220;%s&#8221; inlin','Quick&nbsp;Edit'=>'Yara&nbsp;Ṣatunkọ','Enabled'=>'Ti muu ṣiṣẹ','All'=>'Gbogbo','Quick Edit'=>'Ṣatunkọ Yara','Update'=>'Imudojuiwọn','Cancel'=>'Fagilee','Add support for custom fields in the author profiles.'=>'Fi atilẹyin fun awọn aaye aṣa ninu awọn profaili onkọwe.','Author Field'=>'Field onkọwe','Custom Field updated.'=>'Àwọn ààyè aṣa ti ṣe imudojuiwọn.','Custom Field published.'=>'Àwọn ààyè aṣa ti tẹjade.','Custom Field saved.'=>'Àwọn ààyè aṣa ti fipamọ.','Custom Field submitted.'=>'Àwọn ààyè aṣa ti fi ránṣẹ.','Custom Field'=>'Àwọn ààyè aṣa','Custom Fields'=>'Àwọn ààyè aṣa','Details'=>'Alaye','Field Status'=>'Ipele Ipo','Field Slug'=>'Ipele Slug','The slug is used in code to reference this author field. It is all lowercase and contains only letters, numbers, and hyphens.'=>'Slug ni a lo ninu koodu lati tọka si aaye onkọwe yii. O wa ni gbogbo lẹta kekere ati pe o ni awọn lẹta, awọn nọmba, ati awọn hyphens nikan.','Field Type'=>'Iru Ipele','Social Profile?'=>'Profaili Awujọ?','This feature will add the SameAs property to this link so that search engines realize that the social profile is connected to this author.'=>'Iṣẹ yii yoo fi ohun-ini SameAs kun si ọna asopọ yii ki awọn ẹrọ wiwa le mọ pe profaili awujọ jẹ asopọ si onkọwe yii.','Add a Schema.org property to this field. Examples include alumniOf, worksFor, and birthPlace. %1$sClick here for documentation.%2$s'=>'Fi ohun-ini Schema.org kun si aaye yii. Awọn apẹẹrẹ pẹlu alumniOf, worksFor, ati birthPlace. %1$sTẹ nibi fun iwe afọwọkọ.%2$s','Show in REST API'=>'Fihan ninu REST API','Yes'=>'Bẹẹni','Control whether this field is included in REST API responses.'=>'Ṣakoso boya aaye yii wa ni afikun ninu awọn idahun REST API.','Open Link in New Tab'=>'Ṣii ọna asopọ ninu taabu tuntun','This feature will add the target=”_blank” attribute to your link.'=>'Iṣẹ-ṣiṣe yii yoo fi ohun-ini target=”_blank” kun ọna ọna rẹ.','Link Rel'=>'Asopọ Rel','Requirement'=>'Ibeere','Description'=>'Apejuwe','This description appears under the fields and helps users understand their choice.'=>'Apejuwe yii han ni isalẹ awọn aaye ati pe o ṣe iranlọwọ fun awọn olumulo lati ni oye yiyan wọn.','Status'=>'Ipo','Type'=>'Iru','Job Title'=>'Iṣẹ akọle','With PublishPress Authors Pro, you can add new fields for social networks and more.'=>'Pẹlu PublishPress Authors Pro, o le fi awọn aaye tuntun kun fun awọn nẹtiwọọki awujọ ati diẹ sii.','Field Order updated.'=>'Ilana aṣẹ ti ni imudojuiwọn.','Facebook'=>'Facebook','Please enter the full URL to your Facebook profile.'=>'Jọwọ tẹ URL kikun si profaili Facebook rẹ.','X'=>'X','Please enter the full URL to your X profile.'=>'Jọwọ tẹ URL kikun si profaili X rẹ.','Instagram'=>'Instagram','Please enter the full URL to your Instagram page.'=>'Jọwọ tẹ URL kikun si oju-iwe Instagram rẹ.','LinkedIn'=>'LinkedIn','Please enter the full URL to your LinkedIn profile.'=>'Jọwọ tẹ URL kikun si profaili LinkedIn rẹ.','YouTube'=>'YouTube','Please enter the full URL to your YouTube channel.'=>'Jọwọ tẹ URL kikun si ikanni YouTube rẹ.','TikTok'=>'TikTok','Please enter the full URL to your TikTok profile.'=>'Jọwọ tẹ URL kikun si profaili TikTok rẹ.','Author List'=>'Akojọ Onkọwe','Add support for author list.'=>'Fi atilẹyin fun akojọ onkọwe.','Author Lists'=>'Akojọ Onkọwe','Settings updated successfully.'=>'Eto ti ṣe imudojuiwọn ni aṣeyọri.','Author List deleted successfully.'=>'Akojọ Onkọwe ti paarẹ ni aṣeyọri.','Author List restored from the Trash.'=>'Akojọ Onkọwe ti tún pada wa lati Ibi idalẹjọ.','Author List moved to the Trash.'=>'Akojọ Onkọwe ti gbe lọ si Ibi idalẹjọ.','Add New'=>'Ṣe afikun Tuntun','Search results for &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'%s: wa awọn ọrọ-ọrọ','Search Author Lists'=>'Wa Awọn atokọ Akọwe','Preview'=>'Ṣayẹwo','Users'=>'Awọn olumulo','Options'=>'Awọn aṣayan','The original size of the uploaded image'=>'Iwọn atilẹba ti aworan ti a gbe silẹ','Large-sized image (1024px by 1024px)'=>'Aworan ti iwọn nla (1024px nipasẹ 1024px)','Medium-large image (768px)'=>'Aworan alabọde-nla (768px)','Medium-sized image (300px by 300px)'=>'Aworan alabọde (300px nipasẹ 300px)','Small-sized image (150px by 150px)'=>'