u sẹyin, 6 oṣu sẹyin, 1 ọdun sẹyin ati bẹbẹ lọ.','Show Search Box'=>'Fi Han Apoti Iwadi','Add Search Box to Author Lists'=>'Fi apoti wiwa kun awọn akojọ onkọwe','Author Pro allows you to add a search box to the Authors List. You can also show a dropdown menu that allows users to search on specific author fields.'=>'Author Pro gba ọ laaye lati fi apoti wiwa kun si Atokọ awọn Onkọwe. O tun le fi akojọ aṣayan ti o mu ki awọn olumulo wa lori awọn aaye onkọwe pato han.','Search Field Dropdown'=>'Ibi Iwadi Dropdown','You can also show a dropdown menu that allows users to search on specific author fields.'=>'O tun le fi akojọ aṣayan ti o mu ki awọn olumulo wa lori awọn aaye onkọwe pato han.','Author Recent List'=>'Akojọ Recent ti Onkọwe','Author Index List'=>'Atokọ Iforukọsilẹ onkọwe','Edit Author List'=>'Ṣatunkọ Atokọ Onkọwe','Add Author List'=>'Fi Atokọ Onkọwe kun','Save Changes'=>'Fipamọ Awọn ayipada','Dynamic Shortcode'=>'Koodu Kukuru Alailowaya','Static Shortcode'=>'Koodu Iboju','Select some options'=>'Yan diẹ ninu awọn aṣayan','Select Users'=>'Yan Awọn olumulo','Select Author Category'=>'Yan Ẹka Onkọwe','This is a quick preview of this Author List. Test on frontend pages to see exactly how it looks with your theme.'=>'Eyi jẹ iworan iyara ti Atokọ Onkọwe yii. Danwo lori awọn oju-iwe iwaju lati rii pato bi o ṣe n wo pẹlu akori rẹ.','Invalid form'=>'Fọọmu ti ko tọ','AuthorList'=>'Akojọ Onkọwe','All %s'=>'Gbogbo %s','Trash %s'=>'Ibi idọti %s','No author list avaliable in the selected view.'=>'Ko si atokọ onkọwe ti o wa ninu iwo ti a yan.','Trash'=>'Ibi idọti','Restore'=>'Da pada','Delete Permanently'=>'Pa lailai','Author Pages'=>'Ojú-iwe Onkọwe','Add support for author pages.'=>'Fi atilẹyin fun awọn oju-iwe onkọwe.','Author Bio'=>'Bio Onkọwe','Author Page Title'=>'Ak标题 Ojú-iwe Onkọwe','Migrate Byline Data'=>'Ṣe irinna Data Byline','Add migration option for Byline'=>'Ṣe afikun aṣayan gbigbe fun Byline','Collecting data for the migration...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ ikojọpọ data fun gbigbe ...','Error: '=>'Aṣiṣe: ','Done! Byline data was copied and you can deactivate the plugin.'=>'Ṣe! Awọn data byline ti daakọ ati pe o le mu afikun naa ṣiṣẹ.','Copying authors\' data...'=>'Nṣiṣẹda data awọn onkọwe...','Deactivating Byline...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ Byline...','Done! Byline is deactivated.'=>'Ṣe! Byline ti wa ni mu ṣiṣẹ.','Deactivate Byline'=>'Tẹsiwaju Byline','Copy Byline Data'=>'Daakọ Alaye Byline','Migrate Bylines Data'=>'Ṣe irinna Data Bylines','Add migration option for Bylines'=>'Ṣe afikun aṣayan gbigbe fun Bylines','Done! Bylines data was copied and you can deactivate the plugin.'=>'Ṣe! Awọn data bylines ti daakọ ati pe o le mu afikun naa ṣiṣẹ.','Deactivating Bylines...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ Bylines...','Done! Bylines is deactivated.'=>'Ṣe! Bylines ti wa ni mu ṣiṣẹ.','Deactivate Bylines'=>'Tẹsiwaju Bylines','Copy Bylines Data'=>'Daakọ Alaye Bylines','Debug'=>'Debug','Add debug information for the plugin'=>'Ṣe afikun alaye itupalẹ fun plugin','Authors Debug'=>'Iṣakoso Awọn Onkọwe','Default Layouts'=>'Aiyẹyẹ Awọn Ilana','Authors Index'=>'Ìkàwé Awọn Onkọwe','Authors Recent'=>'Awọn Onkọwe Recent','Divi Integration'=>'Isopọ Divi','Add compatibility with the Divi Theme Builder'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Divi Theme Builder','Edit Flow Integration'=>'Ṣatunkọ Isopọ Iṣan','Add compatibility with the Edit Flow plugin'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Edit Flow plugin','Elementor Integration'=>'Isopọ Elementor','Add compatibility with the Elementor and Elementor Pro page builder'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Elementor ati Elementor Pro page builder','Generatepress Integration'=>'Ìṣàkóso Generatepress','Add compatibility with the Generatepress theme'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Generatepress theme','Genesis Integration'=>'Ìṣàkóso Genesis','Add compatibility with the Genesis framework'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Genesis framework','Authors Settings'=>'Awọn eto Onkọwe','Features'=>'Àwọn Àmúyẹ','Feel free to select only the features you need.'=>'Maa ṣe é ṣiyemeji lati yan awọn ààmú ti o nilo nikan.','Enabled features'=>'Awọn ẹya ti a muu ṣiṣẹ','Recommendations for you'=>'Awọn Iyanjẹ fun ọ','Showcase your Authors with PublishPress Blocks'=>'Ṣe afihan Awọn onkọwe rẹ pẹlu PublishPress Blocks','PublishPress Blocks is a free plugin with full support for PublishPress Authors.'=>'PublishPress Blocks jẹ afikun ọfẹ pẹlu atilẹyin kikun fun PublishPress Authors.','Install this plugin to showcase content by your Authors.'=>'Fi plugin yii sori lati fi akoonu han nipasẹ awọn Onkowe rẹ.','Use the Content Display block to show your posts in many beautiful layouts.'=>'Lo bulọọki Ifihan Akọ content lati fi awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ han ni ọpọlọpọ awọn apẹrẹ ẹlẹwa.','PublishPress Blocks has over 20 extra Gutenberg blocks including accordions, galleries, tables, and more.'=>'PublishPress Blocks ni ju 20 awọn bulọọki Gutenberg afikun pẹlu awọn akordeon, awọn ile-iṣọ, awọn tabili, ati diẹ sii.','Click here to install PublishPress Blocks'=>'Tẹ nibi lati fi sori ẹrọ PublishPress Blocks','Migrate Molongui Data'=>'Ṣe irinna Data Molongui','Add migration option for Molongui Authorship'=>'Ṣe afikun aṣayan gbigbe fun Molongui Authorship','Done! Molongui Authorship data was copied and you can deactivate the plugin.'=>'Ṣe! Awọn data Molongui Authorship ti daakọ ati pe o le mu afikun naa ṣiṣẹ.','Migrating data...'=>'N ṣe irinna data...','Deactivating Molongui Authorship...'=>'Nṣiṣẹda Molongui Onkọwe...','Done! Molongui Authorship is deactivated.'=>'Ṣe! Molongui Authorship ti wa ni mu ṣiṣẹ.','Deactivate Molongui Authorship'=>'Tẹsiwaju Iṣẹ onkọwe Molongui','Copy Molongui Authorship Data'=>'Daakọ Alaye Iwe-ẹri Molongui','This action will copy the authors from the plugin Molongui Authorship allowing you to migrate to PublishPress Authors without losing any data including post author relation. This action can be run multiple times.'=>'Iṣe yii yoo da awọn onkọwe pada lati afikun Molongui Authorship ti o fun laaye lati gö PublishPress Authors laisi padanu eyikeyi data pẹlu ibatan onkọwe ifiweranṣẹ. Iṣe yii le ṣee ṣe ni ọpọlọpọ awọn igba.','It looks like you have Molongui Authorship installed.'=>'O dabi pe o ni Molongui Authorship ti fi sori ẹrọ.','Please click here to migrate to PublishPress Authors'=>'Jọwọ tẹ nibi lati ṣe gbigbe si Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress','Dismiss'=>'Kó','Multiple Authors'=>'Ọpọlọpọ Awon Onkọwe','Pages'=>'Awọn oju-iwe','Author Profile'=>'Profaili Onkọwe','Settings'=>'Eto','Enable PublishPress Authors for these post types:'=>'Muu Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress ṣiṣẹ fun awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ wọnyi:','Post types to display on the author\'s profile page:'=>'Iru ifiweranṣẹ lati ṣe afihan lori oju-iwe profaili onkọwe:','Roles available for Author Profiles:'=>'Awọn iṣẹ ti o wa fun Awọn profaili Akọwe:','Automatically create author profiles:'=>'Ṣe awin awọn profaili onkọwe laifọwọyi:','Show username in the search field:'=>'Fihan orukọ olumulo ninu aaye ìwádìí:','Default author for new posts:'=>'Onkọwe aiyẹyẹ fun awọn ifiweranṣẹ tuntun:','Fallback user for Guest Authors:'=>'Olumulo pada fun Awọn Onkọwe Alejo:','Remove single author map restriction:'=>'Yọ idena maapu onkọwe kan:','Show above the content:'=>'Fihan loke akoonu:','Show below the content:'=>'Fihan ni isalẹ akoonu:','Show Author Box selection:'=>'Fihan yiyan Apoti Onkọwe:','Disable the "Authors" box when using "Quick Edit":'=>'Pa àkọsílẹ "Awon Onkọwe" ti a nlo "Ṣatunkọ Yara":','Default Layout:'=>'Aiyẹyẹ Ilana:','Title for the author box:'=>'Akole fun apoti onkọwe:','Color scheme:'=>'Ẹya awọ:','Show email link:'=>'Fihan ọna ọna imeeli:','Show site link:'=>'Fihan ọna asopọ aaye:','Font Awesome icons:'=>'Àwọn aami Font Awesome:','Enable author pages:'=>'Mú awọn oju-iwe onkọwe ṣiṣẹ:','Author pages posts limit:'=>'Iye ifiweranṣẹ oju-iwe onkọwe:','Author pages layout:'=>'Ilana oju-iwe onkọwe:','Grid layout column:'=>'Àtẹjáde grid àkójọpọ:','Show author bio:'=>'Fihan bio onkọwe:','Author bio layout:'=>'àtúnṣe bio onkọwe:','Show author page title:'=>'Fihan akọle oju-iwe onkọwe:','Author pages excerpt ellipsis:'=>'Akojọpọ oju-iwe onkọwe ellipsis:','Author pages title header:'=>'Akọle akọle oju-iwe onkọwe:','Author post title header:'=>'Akọle akọle ifiweranṣẹ onkọwe:','Show featured image:'=>'Fihan aworan ti a ṣe afihan:','Link featured image to post:'=>'So aworan ti a ṣe afihan pọ si ifiweranṣẹ:','Featured image custom width:'=>'Iwọn ti aworan ti a ṣe afihan:','Featured image custom height:'=>'Iga ti aworan ti a ṣe afihan:','Show excerpt:'=>'Fihan akopọ:','Show authors:'=>'Fihan awọn onkọwe:','Show post date:'=>'Fihan ọjọ ifiweranṣẹ:','Show comment counts:'=>'Fihan iye awọn asọye:','Show category:'=>'Fihan ẹka:','Show tags:'=>'Fihan awọn afi:','Show read more link:'=>'Fihan ọna ọna ka siwaju:','Enable Guest Author With No User Account'=>'Muu Onkọwe Alejo ṣiṣẹ Pẹlu Akọọlẹ Olumulo Tí Kò Ní','Enable Guest Author With User Account'=>'Muu Onkọwe Alejo ṣiṣẹ Pẹlu Akọọlẹ Olumulo','Allow users to opt out of Author Boxes'=>'Gba awọn olumulo laaye lati yọkuro ninu awọn Apo Onkọwe','Boxed legacy layout Author Box:'=>'Ipele apoti atijọ Ipe Onkọwe:','Centered legacy layout Author Box:'=>'Ipele apoti atijọ Ipe Onkọwe:','Inline legacy layout Author Box:'=>'Ni ila atijọ aṣa Awoṣe Onkowe:','Inline avatar legacy layout Author Box:'=>'Ni ila avatar atijọ aṣa Awoṣe Onkowe:','Simple list legacy layout Author Box:'=>'Atokọ Rọrun ti atunto atijọ Apo Onkọwe:','Disabled because add_post_type_support(\'%1$s\', \'%2$s\') is included in a loaded file.'=>'Ti pa nitori add_post_type_support(\'%1$s\', \'%2$s\') wa ninu faili ti a gbe wọle.','This will display the authors box at the top of the content.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan apoti awọn onkọwe ni oke akoonu.','This will display the authors box at the end of the content.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan apoti awọn onkọwe ni ipari akoonu.','Allow users to choose which Author Box is used on each post.'=>'Gba awọn olumulo laaye lati yan iru Apo Onkọwe wo ni a lo lori ọkọọkan ifiweranṣẹ.','Single'=>'Ẹyọkan','Plural'=>'Ipo','Authors Box'=>'Apoti Awọn Onkọwe','With this shortcode you can display the author box in any part of the content. '=>'Pẹlu shortcode yii o le fi apoti onkọwe han ni eyikeyi apakan ti akoonu.','You can specify layout by using author boxes layout slug. You can see full details of each layout option %1$s in this guide %2$s.'=>'O le ṣalaye apẹrẹ nipa lilo slug apẹrẹ apoti onkọwe. O le rii awọn alaye kikun ti gbogbo aṣayan apẹrẹ %1$s ninu itọsọna yii %2$s.','You can also decide whether or not to show the main title, using %1$s or %2$s .'=>'O tun le pinnu boya lati fi akọle pataki han, lilo %1$s tabi %2$s.','You can load the authors for a specific post, even if you are not in that post currently. For example, this shortcode will load the authors for the post with the ID of 32.'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe fun ifiweranṣẹ kan, paapaa ti o ko ba wa ninu ifiweranṣẹ yẹn ni akoko yii. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe awọn onkọwe fun ifiweranṣẹ pẹlu ID ti 32.','You can load the authors for a specific user by providing the user id. For example, this shortcode will load the author with user id of 32'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe fun olumulo kan pato nipa fifun ID olumulo. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe onkọwe pẹlu ID olumulo ti 32','You can load the authors for a specific author by providing the author term id for both guest and user author. For example, this shortcode will load the author with term id of 32'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe fun onkọwe kan pato nipa fifun ID ọrọ onkọwe fun mejeeji alejo ati onkọwe olumulo. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe onkọwe pẹlu ID ọrọ ti 32','If you are having problems showing PublishPress Authors on author profile pages, you can use this shortcode below. The argument %s forces the plugin to retrieve the Author from the profile page and not any other posts on the same screen.'=>'Ti o ba ni iṣoro lati fi han awọn Onkọwe PublishPress lori awọn oju-iwe profaili onkọwe, o le lo shortcode yii ni isalẹ. Iṣeduro %s n ṣiṣẹ plugin naa lati gba Onkọwe lati oju-iwe profaili ati kii ṣe eyikeyi awọn ifiweranṣẹ miiran lori iboju kanna.','There is one final option to mention. This is mostly useful if you\'re using a theme or page builder to customize the Author profile pages you find at URLs such as /author/username/. You can use the following shortcode on the authors page to display the profile of the current author. You just need to add the parameter %s.'=>'Iṣeduro ikẹhin kan wa lati mẹnuba. Eyi jẹ pupọ wulo ti o ba nlo akori tabi oluṣeto oju-iwe lati ṣe akanṣe awọn oju-iwe profaili Onkọwe ti o rii ni awọn URL bi /author/username/. O le lo shortcode atẹle lori oju-iwe awọn onkọwe lati fi han profaili onkọwe lọwọlọwọ. O kan nilo lati fi kun paramita %s.','You can load the authors belonging to a specific author categories by providing the category slug or slugs separated by comma for more than one category.'=>'O le gbe awọn onkọwe ti o jẹ ti awọn ẹka onkọwe pato nipa fifi slug ẹka tabi awọn slugs ti a ya sọtọ nipa koma fun diẹ ẹ sii ju ẹka kan lọ.','Authors Data'=>'Data Awọn Onkọwe','With this shortcode you can display the author names or any profile field in any part of the content.'=>'Pẹlu shortcode yii o le fi han awọn orukọ onkọwe tabi eyikeyi aaye profaili ni eyikeyi apakan ti akoonu.','The authors data shortcode accepts field parameter such as: %1$s %2$s %3$s %4$s %5$s %6$s %7$s. You can see full details and parameters %8$s in this guide %9$s.'=>'Shortcode data awọn onkọwe gba paramita aaye gẹgẹbi: %1$s %2$s %3$s %4$s %5$s %6$s %7$s. O le wo awọn alaye kikun ati awọn paramita %8$s ninu itọsọna yii %9$s.','You can also specify the separator to be used for mulitple authors data.'=>'O tun le ṣalaye akọtọ ti a yoo lo fun data awọn onkọwe pupọ.','You can retrieve a specific author by providing the author\'s term ID. For example, this shortcode will load the author with the term ID of 102.'=>'O le gba onkọwe pato nipa fifi ID ọrọ onkọwe naa. Fun apẹẹrẹ, shortcode yii yoo gbe onkọwe pẹlu ID ọrọ ti 102.','You can also decide to return an array list of authors by using user_objects="true" which will return all the authors object data as an array. You can check full details and sample usage %2$s in this guide%3$s.'=>'O tun le pinnu lati da pada atokọ awọn onkọwe nipa lilo user_objects="true" eyiti yoo da gbogbo awọn data onkọwe pada gẹgẹ bi atokọ. O le ṣayẹwo awọn alaye kikun ati awọn apẹẹrẹ lilo %2$s ninu itọsọna yii%3$s.','You can retrieve authors belonging to a specific Author Category by providing the category slug or slugs. Separate multiple slugs with a comma.'=>'O le gba awọn onkọwe ti o jẹ ti ẹka Onkọwe pato nipa fifi slug ẹka tabi awọn slugs. Ya sọtọ awọn slugs mẹta pẹlu koma.','With this shortcode, you can show all the authors together in a single display.'=>'Pẹlu shortcode yii, o le fi han gbogbo awọn onkọwe papo ni ifihan kan.','You can specify layout by using author boxes layout slug. You can see full details of each layout option %1$s in this guide %2$s. %3$s %4$s This shortcode also provides two custom layouts: %5$s %6$s.'=>'O le tọka iṣeto nipa lilo slug iṣeto awọn apo onkọwe. O le wo awọn alaye kikun ti gbogbo aṣayan iṣeto %1$s ninu itọsọna yii %2$s. %3$s %4$s Shortcode yii tun n pese awọn iṣeto adani meji: %5$s %6$s.','You can define the number of layout columns by using %1$s to show authors in 2 column.'=>'O le ṣe alaye nọmba awọn ọwọn iṣeto nipa lilo %1$s lati fi han awọn onkọwe ni awọn ọwọn 2.','You can choose the number of authors per page using %1$s . %2$s Pagination will be automatically added if required.'=>'O le yan nọmba awọn onkọwe fun oju-iwe kan nipa lilo %1$s. %2$s Iṣakojọpọ yoo jẹ afikun laifọwọyi ti o ba nilo.','You can limit the result to only authors who are assigned to posts by using %1$s . %2$s Alternatively, use %3$s to show all authors, including those without any posts.'=>'O le ni idiwọ abajade si awọn onkọwe nikan ti a yan si awọn ifiweranṣẹ nipa lilo %1$s. %2$s Ni omiiran, lo %3$s lati fi han gbogbo awọn onkọwe, pẹlu awọn ti ko ni awọn ifiweranṣẹ.','You can limit the result to only guest authors by using %1$s . %2$s Alternatively, %3$s will show only authors with a WordPress account.'=>'O le ni idiwọ abajade si awọn onkọwe alejo nikan nipa lilo %1$s. %2$s Ni omiiran, %3$s yoo fi han awọn onkọwe nikan pẹlu akọọlẹ WordPress kan.','If you are using the authors_recent layout, you can define the number of columns by using %1$s .'=>'Ti o ba nlo iṣeto authors_recent, o le ṣe alaye nọmba awọn ọwọn nipa lilo %1$s.','For authors_index layout, you can group user by profile field by using %1$s .'=>'Fun iṣeto authors_index, o le kó awọn olumulo pọ nipasẹ aaye profaili nipa lilo %1$s.','To order the results based on post count, use %1$s . To order the results by name, use %2$s . Alternatively, you can order by profile fields like %3$s, %4$s etc'=>'Lati paṣẹ awọn abajade da lori nọmba awọn ifiweranṣẹ, lo %1$s. Lati paṣẹ awọn abajade nipasẹ orukọ, lo %2$s. Ni omiiran, o le paṣẹ nipasẹ awọn aaye profaili bii %3$s, %4$s ati bẹbẹ lọ.','To further customize the order of results, use %1$s or %2$s .'=>'Lati tun ṣe akanṣe aṣẹ awọn esi, lo %1$s tabi %2$s .','To display a search box for authors, use %1$s .'=>'Lati ṣe afihan apoti wiwa fun awọn onkọwe, lo %1$s .','You can also show a dropdown menu that allows users to search on specific author fields. You can add fields to the dropdown using %1$s . This requires the search box to be active.'=>'O tun le fi han akojọ aṣayan isalẹ ti o fun awọn olumulo laaye lati wa lori awọn aaye onkọwe pato. O le fi awọn aaye kun si akojọ aṣayan isalẹ nipa lilo %1$s. Eyi nilo ki apoti wiwa jẹ iṣẹ.','You can limit the author list to users with a published post within a specific period using %1$s . This accept english date value like 1 week ago, 1 month ago, 6 months ago, 1 year ago etc.'=>'O le ni idiwọ atokọ onkọwe si awọn olumulo pẹlu ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade laarin akoko pato nipa lilo %1$s. Eyi gba iye ọjọ Gẹẹsi gẹgẹbi 1 ọsẹ sẹyin, 1 oṣu sẹyin, 6 oṣu sẹyin, 1 ọdun sẹyin ati bẹbẹ lọ.','Copied!'=>'Ti a daakọ!','Click To Copy!'=>'Tẹ lati Daakọ!','Select roles'=>'Yan awọn ipa','Choose which WordPress user roles can be selected using the "Registered Author With User Account" option for author profiles.'=>'Yan iru awọn ipa olumulo WordPress wo ni a le yan nipa lilo aṣayan "Onkọwe Ti a Forukọsilẹ Pẹlu Iṣẹ olumulo" fun awọn profaili onkọwe.','Author profiles can be mapped to WordPress user accounts. This option allows you to automatically create author profiles when users are created in these roles. You can also do this for existing users by clicking the "Create PublishPress Authors Profiles for all users in a role" button in the Maintenance tab.'=>'Awọn profaili onkọwe le jẹ asopọ si awọn iroyin olumulo WordPress. Eto yii n jẹ ki o ṣẹda awọn profaili onkọwe laifọwọyi nigbati awọn olumulo ba ṣẹda ni awọn ipa wọnyi. O tun le ṣe eyi fun awọn olumulo ti o wa tẹlẹ nipa titẹ bọtini "Ṣẹda Awọn Profaili Onkọwe PublishPress fun gbogbo awọn olumulo ni ipa" ninu taabu Itọju.','If the Author is mapped to a WordPress user, this will display the authors\' "Display name" and their "Username". The default is to show only the "Display name". Showing the "Username" is useful if you have several authors with similar names.'=>'Ti a ba sopọ onkọwe si olumulo WordPress, eyi yoo fi hàn "Orukọ Ifihan" ti awọn onkọwe ati "Orukọ olumulo" wọn. Aiyipada ni lati fi hàn nikan "Orukọ Ifihan". Ifihan "Orukọ olumulo" jẹ wulo ti o ba ni ọpọlọpọ awọn onkọwe pẹlu awọn orukọ ti o jọra.','Allow authors to be created without a real user account.'=>'Gba laaye lati ṣẹda awọn onkọwe laisi iroyin olumulo gidi.','Show a profile checkbox allowing Authors to be excluded from Author Boxes.'=>'Fihan apoti akọsilẹ kan ti ngbanilaaye awọn Onkọwe lati wa ni yọkuro lati awọn apoti onkọwe.','Allow authors to be created without a connected user account.'=>'Gba laaye lati ṣẹda awọn onkọwe laisi iroyin olumulo ti o ni asopọ.','If enabled, PublishPress Authors will replace the default WordPress author pages.'=>'Ti a ba mu ṣiṣẹ, Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress yoo rọpo awọn oju-iwe onkọwe aiyipada WordPress.','Please note this feature will not work for all themes.'=>'Jọwọ ṣe akiyesi pe ẹya yii ko ni ṣiṣẹ fun gbogbo awọn akori.','Click here for more details.'=>'Tẹ nibi fun alaye diẹ sii.','View sample Author Page'=>'Wo àpẹẹrẹ Ojúewé Onkọwe','List'=>'Atokọ','Grid'=>'Grid','Allow User to Choose'=>'Gba laaye Olumulo lati Yan','First Name Last Name'=>'Orukọ Akọkọ Orukọ Ikẹhin','Last Name First Name'=>'Orukọ Ikẹhin Orukọ akọkọ','This avatar will be used as default avatar instead of gravatar where no custom avatar is added to profile.'=>'Avatar yii yoo lo gẹgẹbi avatar aiyipada dipo gravatar nibiti avatar aṣa ko ba ṣafikun si profaili.','This will display the author bio.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan bio onkọwe.','Select option'=>'Yan aṣayan','This is useful if you use legacy shortcode %s'=>'Eyi wulo ti o ba lo koodu kukuru atijọ %s','This will display the featured image.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan aworan ti a ṣe afihan.','This will make the featured image clickable and link to the post.'=>'Eyi yoo jẹ ki aworan ti a ṣe afihan le tẹ ati so pọ si ifiweranṣẹ.','This will display author page title.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan akọle oju-iwe onkọwe.','This will display the excerpt.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan akopọ naa.','This will allows you map a WordPress user to more than one author. Don\'t use this feature unless requested to do so by the PublishPress team. This plugin works better when authors and users are paired one-to-one.'=>'Eyi yoo jẹ ki o sopọ olumulo WordPress si ju onkọwe kan lọ. Maṣe lo ẹya yii ayafi ti a beere lọwọ rẹ lati ṣe bẹ nipasẹ ẹgbẹ PublishPress. Ẹya yii ṣiṣẹ dara julọ nigbati awọn onkọwe ati awọn olumulo ba ni ibamu ọkan-si-ọkan.','This will display the authors.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan awọn onkọwe.','This will display the published date.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan ọjọ ti a tẹjade.','This will display the comment count.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan iye awọn asọye.','This will display the categories.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan awọn ẹka.','This will display the tags.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan awọn aami.','This will display the read more link.'=>'Yi yoo ṣe afihan ọna asopọ ka siwaju.','This setting may be disabled for users who can not edit others posts.'=>'Iṣeto yii le jẹ ti a ko ṣiṣẹ fun awọn olumulo ti ko le ṣatunkọ awọn ifiweranṣẹ miiran.','Search for a fallback author'=>'Wa fun akọwe itẹsiwaju','If you only have Guest Authors selected for a post, this user may be used as a fallback. WordPress sometimes requires a WordPress user to be assigned to each post. This user will not be visible on the front of your site.'=>'Ti o ba ni awọn Onkọwe Alejo nikan ti a yan fun ifiweranṣẹ, olumulo yii le ṣee lo gẹgẹbi fallback. WordPress nigbagbogbo nilo ki a fi olumulo WordPress si iroyin kọọkan. Olumulo yii ko ni han lori iwaju aaye rẹ.','This will display the authors email in the author box.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan imeeli awọn onkọwe ni apoti onkọwe.','This will display the authors site in the author box.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe afihan aaye ayelujara awọn onkọwe ni apoti onkọwe.','This will load Font Awesome icons for use in Author Boxes.'=>'Yi yoo gba awọn aami Font Awesome lati lo ninu Awọn Apoti Onkọwe.','This will remove the Authors Box in "Quick Edit".'=>'Yi yoo yọ Apoti Onkọwe ni "Ṣatunkọ Pẹlẹpẹlẹ".','Create PublishPress Authors Profiles for all post authors'=>'Ṣẹda Awọn Profaili Onkọwe PublishPress fun gbogbo awọn onkọwe ifiweranṣẹ','If a WordPress user is the author of a post, but does not have a PublishPress Authors profile, this will automatically create a profile for them.'=>'Ti olumulo WordPress ba jẹ onkọwe ti ifiweranṣẹ kan, ṣugbọn ko ni profaili Onkọwe PublishPress, eyi yoo ṣẹda profaili fun wọn laifọwọyi.','Click here for documentation'=>'Tẹ nibi fun iwe aṣẹ','Create missing PublishPress Authors profiles'=>'Ṣẹda awọn profaili Onkọwe PublishPress ti o padanu','Create PublishPress Authors Profiles for all users in a role'=>'Ṣẹda Awọn Profaili Onkọwe PublishPress fun gbogbo awọn olumulo ninu ipa kan','This will find all the users in a role and create author profiles for them. You can choose the roles using the "Automatically create author profiles" setting.'=>'Eyi yoo wa gbogbo awọn olumulo ni ipa kan ki o ṣẹda awọn profaili onkọwe fun wọn. O le yan awọn ipa nipa lilo eto "Ṣẹda awọn profaili onkọwe laifọwọyi".','Create PublishPress Authors profiles'=>'Ṣẹda awọn profaili Onkọwe PublishPress','Synchronize PublishPress Authors Fields and user profile fields'=>'Sopọ Awọn aaye Onkọwe PublishPress ati awọn aaye profaili olumulo','This will update all the author profiles in PublishPress Authors to match the default WordPress fields for each user.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe imudojuiwọn gbogbo awọn profaili onkọwe ni Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress lati ba awọn aaye aiyipada WordPress mu fun olumulo kọọkan.','Synchronize the author and user URLs'=>'Sopọ awọn URL onkọwe ati olumulo','This will update all the Author URLs in PublishPress Authors to match the default WordPress URLs for each user.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣe imudojuiwọn gbogbo awọn URL Onkọwe ni Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress lati ba awọn URL aiyipada WordPress mu fun olumulo kọọkan.','Create Author Categories'=>'Ṣẹda Awọn Ẹka Onkọwe','This will create author categories table if missing and add default categories.'=>'Eyi yoo ṣẹda tabili awọn ẹka onkọwe ti o ba ṣofo ki o si fi awọn ẹka aiyipada kun.','Copy Co-Authors Plus Data'=>'Daakọ Alaye Co-Authors Plus','This action will copy the authors from the plugin Co-Authors Plus allowing you to migrate to PublishPress Authors without losing any data. This action can be run multiple times.'=>'Igbese yii yoo daakọ awọn onkọwe lati plugin Co-Authors Plus ti o fun ọ laaye lati kọja si Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress laisi padanu eyikeyi data. Igbese yii le ṣee ṣe ni igba pupọ.','Delete Connections Between Author Profiles and Users'=>'Pa Awọn Asopọ laarin Awọn Profaili Onkọwe ati Awọn olumulo','This action can reset the PublishPress Authors data before using other maintenance options. It will delete all author profiles that are mapped to a WordPress user account. This will not delete the WordPress user accounts, but any links between the posts and author profiles will be lost.'=>'Igbese yii le tun ṣe data Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress ṣaaju ki o to lo awọn aṣayan itọju miiran. Yoo pa gbogbo awọn profaili onkọwe ti a ti sopọ mọ iroyin olumulo WordPress. Eyi kii yoo pa awọn iroyin olumulo WordPress, ṣugbọn eyikeyi awọn ọna asopọ laarin awọn ifiweranṣẹ ati awọn profaili onkọwe yoo sọnu.','Delete all authors mapped to users'=>'Pa gbogbo awọn onkọwe ti a ti ṣe iha si awọn olumulo','Delete Guest Authors'=>'Pa Awọn Onkọwe Alejo','This action can reset the PublishPress Authors data before using other maintenance options. Guest authors are author profiles that are not mapped to a WordPress user account. This action will delete all guest authors.'=>'Igbese yii le tun ṣe data Awọn Onkọwe PublishPress ṣaaju ki o to lo awọn aṣayan itọju miiran. Awọn onkọwe alejo ni awọn profaili onkọwe ti ko ni asopọ si iroyin olumulo WordPress. Igbese yii yoo pa gbogbo awọn onkọwe alejo.','Delete all guest authors'=>'Pa gbogbo awọn onkọwe alejo','Please be careful clicking these buttons. Before clicking, we recommend taking a site backup in case anything goes wrong.'=>'Jọwọ ṣọra nigbati o ba n tẹ awọn bọtini wọnyi. Ṣaaju ki o to tẹ, a ṣe iṣeduro lati mu afẹyinti aaye kan ni ọran ti ohunkohun ba ṣẹlẹ.','Author Profiles'=>'Profaili Onkọwe','Integration'=>'Isopọ','Maintenance'=>'Iṣọkan','Advanced'=>'Ijinle','Invalid nonce'=>'Nonce ti ko tọ','Access denied'=>'Iwọle ti kọ','Error. Author terms could not be reseted.'=>'Aṣiṣe. Awọn ọrọ onkọwe ko le ṣe atunṣe.','Maintenance completed successfully.'=>'Iṣẹ itọju ti pari ni aṣeyọri.','Collecting data...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ ikojọpọ data ...','Finishing the process...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ ilana...','Done! %d posts were updated.'=>'Ṣe! %d awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti ni imudojuiwọn.','Updating author field on posts...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ imudojuiwọn aaye onkọwe lori awọn ifiweranṣẹ...','Updated %d of %d posts...'=>'Imudojuiwọn %d ti %d awọn ifiweranṣẹ...','Sync author and user URLs'=>'Sopọ awọn URL onkọwe ati olumulo','Done! %d authors were updated.'=>'Ṣe! %d awọn onkọwe ti ni imudojuiwọn.','Updating authors slug...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ imudojuiwọn slug awọn onkọwe...','Updated %d of %d authors...'=>'Imudojuiwọn %d ti %d awọn onkọwe...','Creating missed post authors....'=>'Ṣiṣẹda awọn onkọwe ifiweranṣẹ ti a padanu....','Copy Co-Authors Plus data'=>'Daakọ alaye Co-Authors Plus','Deactivating Co-uthors Plus...'=>'Nṣiṣẹ Co-authors Plus...','Done! Co-Authors Plus is deactivated.'=>'Ṣe! Co-Authors Plus ti wa ni mu ṣiṣẹ.','Deactivate Co-Authors Plus'=>'Tẹsiwaju Co-Authors Plus','Done! Co-Authors Plus data was copied.'=>'Ṣe! Awọn data Co-Authors Plus ti daakọ.','It looks like you have Co-Authors Plus installed.'=>'O dabi pe o ni Co-Authors Plus ti fi sori ẹrọ.','Please click here and read this guide!'=>'Jọwọ tẹ nibi ki o si ka itọsọna yii!','PublishPress Authors needs a database update for Permissions integration.'=>'PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe nilo imudojuiwọn ibi ipamọ fun isopọmọ Awọn igbanilaaye.','Click to run the update now'=>'Tẹ lati ṣiṣẹ imudojuiwọn bayi','Guest Author cannot login on the site.'=>'Onkọwe alejo ko le wọle si aaye naa.','Polylang Integration'=>'Isopọ Polylang','Enable Polylang Author Translation:'=>'Muu Itumọ Onkọwe Polylang ṣiṣẹ:','Enable translation of author profiles in Polylang.'=>'Muu itumọ awọn profaili onkọwe ni Polylang.','Rank Math Seo Integration'=>'Isopọ Rank Math Seo','Add compatibility with the Rank Math Seo plugin'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Rank Math Seo plugin','Rest API'=>'REST API','Rest API support'=>'Atilẹyin REST API','Guest authors without user accounts is not enabled.'=>'Awọn onkọwe alejo laisi awọn akọkọ olumulo ko ti ṣiṣẹ.','Guest author with user accounts is not enabled.'=>'Onkọwe alejo pẹlu awọn akọkọ olumulo ko ti ṣiṣẹ.','An author with this slug already exists.'=>'Onkọwe pẹlu slug yii tẹlẹ wa.','This WordPress user is already mapped to another author.'=>'Olumulo WordPress yi ti wa ni ipamọ tẹlẹ si onkọwe miiran.','Author was created but could not be retrieved.'=>'Onkọwe ti ṣẹda ṣugbọn a ko le gba.','Author not found.'=>'Onkọwe ko ri.','You cannot edit author mapped to administrator account.'=>'O ko le ṣatunkọ onkọwe ti a ṣe pọ si iroyin alakoso.','You do not have permission to edit this author.'=>'O ko ni aṣẹ lati ṣatunkọ onkọwe yii.','Reviews'=>'Awọn ayẹwo','The SEO Framework Integration'=>'Iṣọpọ SEO Framework','Add compatibility with The SEO Framework plugin.'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu The SEO Framework plugin.','PublishPress Authors Settings'=>'Awọn Eto PublishPress Awọn Onkọwe','There are no PublishPress modules registered'=>'Ko si awọn modulu PublishPress ti a forukọsilẹ','Ultimate_Post Integration'=>'Isopọ Ultimate_Post','Add compatibility with the Ultimate Post plugin'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Ultimate Post plugin','By'=>'Nipa','Ultimate Member Integration'=>'Isopọ Ẹgbẹ Olumulo','Add compatibility with the Ultimate Member plugin'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Ultimate Member plugin','WPEngine Integration'=>'Isopọ WPEngine','Add compatibility with the WPEngine object cache.'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu WPEngine object cache.','Yoast SEO Integration'=>'Isopọ Yoast SEO','Add compatibility with the Yoast SEO plugin'=>'Ṣe afikun ibamu pẹlu Yoast SEO plugin','Comment counts'=>'Iye awọn asọye','Prev'=>'Tẹsiwaju','Next'=>'Tẹle','Post not found for the author'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ ko ri fun onkọwe naa','Published date'=>'Ọjọ ti a tẹjade','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. Thank you!'=>'Tí o bá fẹ́ %1$s jọ̀wọ́ fi %2$s ìdáhùn silẹ fún wa. Ẹ ṣéun!','About'=>'Nipa','Documentation'=>'Iwe Itọsọna','Contact'=>'Kan si','taxonomy general nameAuthors'=>'Awọn onkọwe','taxonomy singular nameAuthor'=>'Onkọwe','Author Box post type name%2$s'=>'%2$s','singular author box post type name%1$s'=>'%1$s','custom layout post type menu name%2$s'=>'%2$s','Custom Field post type name%2$s'=>'%2$s','singular custom field post type name%1$s'=>'%1$s','custom field post type menu name%2$s'=>'%2$s']];